            <div type="a">
                <column>3</column>
                <head/>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The editor notes that the Enquirer, Sentinel, and Dispatch often copy news
                    articles from western Virginia from the Vindicator but either credit them to the
                    Spectator or do not credit them at all. The Sentinel and Enquirer have made the
                    omission once, but the Dispatch frequently fails to credit the articles. The
                    editor calls the situation to the attention of his colleagues at these papers.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
